20	Army Sgt. Maj. Benny Hubbard	<!doctype html>\r\n<html>\r\n  <head>\r\n    <title></title>\r\n    <style>\r\n        img {\r\n            float : right;\r\n            margin: 20px;\r\n            box-shadow: 0 0 4px 4px gray;\r\n            width: 70%;\r\n        }\r\n    </style>\r\n  </head>\r\n  <body>\r\n    <!-- Photo : /static/jengamtandao/images/benny_hubbard.jpg -->\r\n    <img src="/static/jengamtandao/images/benny_hubbard.jpg"/>\r\n    \r\n    <p>\r\n    <b>Stock Photo Description:</b> U.S. Army Sgt. Maj. Benny Hubbard, the district Sgt. Maj. for Gulf Region South, U.S. Army Corps of Engineers, talks with an Iraqi child during the ribbon cutting ceremony for the Salah Hadi Obid Elementary School in Afak, Iraq, Oct. 11, 2006. The construction of the school was funded, contracted and inspected by the U.S. Army Corps of Engineers. (U.S. Air Force photo by Tech. Sgt. Dawn M. Price). Stock photography by Department of Defense Public Domain.\r\n    </p>\r\n    <hr/>\r\n    <b>Copyright:</b> United States Government Works<br/>\r\n    Model Release: No<br/>\r\n    Property Release: No<br/>\r\n    <hr/>\r\n    * This is a public domain image<br/>\r\n    Licensing Stock Photography?<br/>\r\n    Use the Lightbox to save and view photos and images.<br/>\r\n    <hr/>\r\n    High Resolution Version - Help<br/>\r\n    3008 x 1960 Pixels - 17.7 MB<br/>\r\n    10.03" x 6.53" @ 300dpi<br/>\r\n    25.48 cm x 16.59 cm<br/>\r\n    2.1 mb RGB JPEG File<br/>\r\n  </body>\r\n</html>	<!doctype html>\r\n<html>\r\n  <head>\r\n    <title></title>\r\n  </head>\r\n  <body>\r\n    <!-- Photo : /static/jengamtandao/images/benny_hubbard.jpg -->\r\n    \r\n    Stock Photo Description: U.S. Army Sgt. Maj. Benny Hubbard, the district Sgt. Maj. for Gulf Region South, U.S. Army Corps of Engineers, talks with an Iraqi child during the ribbon cutting ceremony for the Salah Hadi Obid Elementary School in Afak, Iraq, Oct. 11, 2006. The construction of the school was funded, contracted and inspe